question: What went well this month? What did I accomplish? How does it make me feel?
What didn’t go so well? How can I improve for next month?
What lessons did I learn this month? How did I grow as a person?
What challenges did I face this month? How did I deal with them?
What am I spending too little or too much time on?
What didn’t go as planned? And how can I improve on it?
Review any goals you set for this month. Did you reach them? Why or why not?
Was there anything holding me back from reaching my goals?
What goals do I have for next month?
List 5 things that made you feel most grateful this month.
What habits did I focus on this month and how did I do?
Which habits should I continue working on next month? Why?
Are there any bad habits I want to work on next month? Make an action plan.
What new habits do I want to try and implement next month? Why?
Overall, am I satisfied with how the month went? Why or why not?
What really matters right now in my life and are my Big Goals still aligned with this?
Are my current Daily Systems aligned with my Big and Checkpoint Goals?
What do I need to cut from my life to progress more efficiently?
